//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Central-Cee.-CREDIT_-Press-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Central-Cee.-CREDIT_-Press-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a>在 Apple Music 1 上推出了自己的广播节目“CRG Radio”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/central-cee-live-in-london-review-alexandra-palace-setlist-photos-3354394">Central Cee 伦敦演唱会：没有噱头，只有刺激</a></strong></li></ul><p>这部由四部分组成的系列节目旨在探索这位说唱歌手的音乐幕后，深入了解他的首张专辑的制作过程，并采访那些迄今为止塑造了他职业生涯的人。</p><p>在其首集中，Trapstar 创始人 Mikey、Lee 和 Will 也将加入 Cench。还将对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/headie-one">Headie One</a> 、Blade Brown 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nemzzz">Nemzzz</a>进行 Facetime 采访，他们将在节目中独家首演新音乐。</p><p> “我们将其称为 CRG 广播电台。” Central Cee 在一份新闻稿中表示。 “我的专辑《Can&#39;t Rush Greatness》的缩写。我和我的朋友们将接管 Apple Music 进行完整的独家演出。我在 Apple Music 上做这件事。这是第一场演出，所以应该是一件大事。”</p><p>第一集将于今晚（12 月 5 日）格林尼治标准时间晚上 7 点在 Apple Music 上直播。你可以<a href="http://apple.co/_CRGRadio" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>收听。 </p><figure id="attachment_3819349" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3819349" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3819349" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Central-Cee-and-Trapstar-cofounders-Mikey-Lee-and-Will.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Central-Cee-and-Trapstar-cofounders-Mikey-Lee-and-Will.-CREDIT_-Press.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Central-Cee-and-Trapstar-cofounders-Mikey-Lee-and-Will.-CREDIT_-Press-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Central-Cee-and-Trapstar-cofounders-Mikey-Lee-and-Will.-CREDIT_-Press-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Central-Cee-and-Trapstar-cofounders-Mikey-Lee-and-W