与电影真实的声音相结合，创造了一种身临其境、令人感动的观看体验，让观众感觉自己身临其境，与乐队一起在场馆里。”</p><p>该纪录片的预告片也已分享，您可以在下面查看。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="成为 Led Zeppelin IMAX 独家 |官方预告片|在 IMAX® 中体验" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZUTLOltEOf8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我们花了五年的时间来回飞越大西洋，搜寻阁楼和地下室，寻找罕见的、未曾见过的电影片段、照片和音乐录音，”编剧兼制片人艾莉森·麦格蒂说。 “然后我们用定制技术转移每一个媒体片段，这样在 IMAX 中，这些 55 年前的片段和音乐看起来和听起来就像是昨天从实验室出来的一样。”</p><p> “我们非常高兴能与 IMAX 和索尼经典影业合作，将这部电影搬上大银幕，面向所有观众，当然包括齐柏林飞艇粉丝，还有所有音乐爱好者以及任何寻求鼓舞人心、令人振奋的故事的人。音乐，”麦戈蒂补充道。</p><p><em>成为齐柏林飞艇乐队</em>是齐柏林飞艇乐队 50 年来首次参与纪录片制作，乐队给予麦克马洪“前所未有的参与”该电影的机会。</p><p>该纪录片的粗略版本<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/led-zeppelin-documentary-becoming-led-zeppelin-set-to-premiere-at-venice-film-festival-3009913">于 2021 年 9 月在威尼斯电影节</a>首映，但此后就再也没有上映过。</p><p>此外，Page 还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/led-zeppelin-icon-jimmy-page-teams-up-with-gibson-to-launch-new-eds-1275-doubleneck-vos-custom-guitar-3819171">推出了一款新的 EDS-1275 Doubleneck VOS 定制吉他，作为​​他与 Gibson 持续合作的一部分</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/new-led-zeppelin-documentary-becoming-led-zeppelin-is-coming-to-imax-in-2025-3819285">新 Led Zeppelin 纪录片《成为 Led Zeppelin》将于 2025 年登陆 IMAX，</a>并在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首发。</p> ;
 1975 年的 Matty Healy 在 Azealia Banks 争吵中说道：“我真的让自己失望了” https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-on-the-azealia-banks-row-i-really-let-myself-down-3819239?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-1975s-matty-healy-on-the-azealia-banks-row-i-really-let-myself-downLaura Molloy Thu, 05 Dec 2024 15:19:34 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3819239 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matty-Healy-and-Azealia-Banks.-CREDIT_-Erika-Goldring_WireImage-and-Lorne-Thomson_Redferns.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matty-Healy-and-Azealia-Banks.-CREDIT_-Erika-Goldring_WireImage-and-Lorne-Thomson_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matty-Healy-and-Azealia-Banks.-CREDIT_-Erika-Goldring_WireImage-and-Lorne-Thomson_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matty-Healy-and-Azealia-Banks.-CREDIT_-Erika-Goldring_WireImage-and-Lorne-Thomson_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matty-Healy-and-Azealia-Banks.-CREDIT_-Erika-Goldring_WireImage-and-Lorne-Thomson_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matty-Healy-and-Azealia-Banks.-CREDIT_-Erika-Goldring_WireImage-and-Lorne-Thomson_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Matty-Healy-and-Azealia-Banks.-CREDIT_-Erika-Goldring_WireImage-and-Lorne-Thomson_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我非常努力地克服这些冲动的自我毁灭性的情绪，而且老实说，我的情绪非常不稳定。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975s-matty-healy-on-the-azealia-banks-row-i-really-let-myself-down-3819239">1975 年的马蒂·希利 (Matty Healy) 在 Azealia Banks 争吵中发表的帖子：“我真的让自己失望了”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-